content: Out of all your ultimate sims this one is probably one of my favourites! But there are a few things that could be fixed. 1: the sensitivity of the camera position, I just touch the screen slightly and the camera view goes crazy! I have grown use to it but at times it gets annoying. 2: when you play as dolphin and you go to eat something, some times they will stay there and keep doing the eating animation and won't stop, that happens to the dolphins when you feed them treats in the den too. 3: the orca scaling is kinda bad, I recently unlocked it and the first thing I noticed was the size difference compared to a regular wild orca, the playable one is tiny like a dolphin and the regular ones are huge! I went to go tame one as my mate and as soon as I tamed one, their huge size decreases by quite a bit. OTHERWISE, this game is great and was definitely worth $1.30! (P.s I hope your next sim will be Ultimate Arctic Simulator 😊)
